  "time_ut": 1656311346,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0daf\u0dda\u0dc1\u0dd3\u0dba \u0dbd\u0dda\u0d9a\u0db8\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dbb \u0d9a\u0dc5\u0dcf\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb.\u0dbd\u0dda \u0dc3\u0dda\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dba\u0ddd \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0ddd\u0db0\u0dba \u0db4\u0dcf\u0dad\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Divisional Secretary's imprisoned Divisional Secretariat employees protest",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Employees of the Matara Divisional Secretariat went on strike today in protest of the detention of Matara Divisional Secretary Kaushalya Kumari who had gone to the Matara General Hospital for medical treatment.",
        "Due to this the people who came to get the services faced severe difficulties.",
        "Employees who marched in front of the Matara District Secretariat requested the Matara Government Agent to provide a just solution to this problem.",
        "Accordingly, several delegates were granted permission to meet the Chief Government Agent of Matara, Mr. Y. Wickramarasiri."
      ],
